10 SECTION 3. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
11 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 567.5c of Title 59, unless there
12 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
13 A. The Oklahoma Board of Nursing shall promulgate rules
14 governing the advertising of health care services by Advanced
15 Practice Registered Nurses to include, but not be limited to, the
16 specialty areas or types of health care services Advanced Practice
17 Registered Nurses may advertise based on their training or
18 experience.
